### API calls

### GET all blogposts

GET http://localhost:3000/api/blogpost HTTP/1.1

### GET a blogpost by ID

GET http://localhost:3000/api/blogpost/2 HTTP/1.1

### POST a blogspot & update the title, body, userId

POST http://localhost:3000/api/blogpost HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "title of blog post",
    "body": "Text of a sample blog post.",
}

### GET user

GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/ HTTP/1.1

### GET user ID

GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/13 HTTP 1.1

### POST user

POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/ HTTP 1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Ted Vinaigrette",
}

### Update an existing blog post

PUT http://localhost:3000/api/blogpost/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "This is a title."
}

### Update an existing user

PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Dan"
}

### Delete a blog post 

DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/blogpost/1 HTTP/1.1


